e_{ssn} &amp;amp;= \lim_{s\to0}sE(s)\\
       &amp;amp;=\lim_{s\to0}s\Phi_{en}(s)N(s)\\
       &amp;amp;=\lim_{s\to0}\frac{sN(s)}{1+G(s)H(s)}
\end{aligned}
